description: V2 Sausage Plant Based Classic British is deliciously juicy, classic British sausages, seasoned with sage, coriander, pepper and nutmeg, perfect for any occasion. Australia's new #1 plant-based meat (based on total KGs sold, latest 12-months to 08/03/2022, Plant-based Meat brands, AU Grocery). Easy to cook, great taste. Good for you, healthy choice. Animal-free, soy-based.At v2, we're all about great tasting food and that's something we can all agree on. Say hello to your newest crowd pleaser! Plant-based v2sausage® Classic British delivers a traditional flavour combination, perfect for all meal occasions from breakfast to dinner. We're Australian-made from soy, with no artificial colours or flavours, non-gmo and with the healthy benefits of protein and fibre. Did we mention that we're also packed with flavour? Enjoy!We're on a mission to feed the planet in a way that takes care of the planet. v2food was founded with a commitment to creating version 2 of food that can sustainably feed the world's rapidly growing population. We believe that food should taste great, whilst being good for you and good for the planet. Eat v2, save the planet!
